Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:22.15,0:00:24.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,得意忘形的傢伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:24.59,0:00:27.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒有預約時間(硬比出V手勢)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:27.56,0:00:30.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,女英雄駕到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:30.43,0:00:33.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,盡情的吃甜點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:33.26,0:00:35.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,忘掉煩人的事吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:36.60,0:00:39.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,ThankYou! 挖到寶了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:39.57,0:00:42.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,招財貓招啊招(客人來吧)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:42.50,0:00:47.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一定能進入你的內心殿堂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:47.81,0:00:50.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,麻煩警報 (踩到地雷)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:50.81,0:00:53.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要有點刺激才行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:54.12,0:00:56.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就算吃海苔時噎到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:56.62,0:00:57.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還是盯著攝影機看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:57.92,0:00:59.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,擺出明星架式
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:59.45,0:01:01.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒問題V手勢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:02.32,0:01:05.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,天使 Rock'n'Roll
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:05.19,0:01:08.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,老套的樂園(啊搖擺搖擺)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:08.26,0:01:13.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,旋轉的宇宙也在跳舞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:13.97,0:01:16.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,火力全開
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:16.91,0:01:18.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,搖搖擺擺跳一跳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:18.81,0:01:19.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,(啊搖擺搖擺)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:19.94,0:01:25.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大家都會變成天使
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:28.18,0:01:29.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哇！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:31.95,0:01:35.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,長官，目前警戒區內沒有發現可疑人物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:36.89,0:01:38.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:38.36,0:01:40.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,繼續加強警戒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:40.43,0:01:41.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:44.13,0:01:47.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個被公佈出去的話他們就完蛋了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:47.14,0:01:49.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是現在還不能安心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:49.47,0:01:52.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他們一定會使出什麼招數
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:52.64,0:01:54.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,職業殺手嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:54.11,0:01:58.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過，這個房間理論上應該只有你跟我進得來吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:58.68,0:02:00.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是這樣沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:01.98,0:02:03.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是什麼聲音?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:03.28,0:02:04.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,從哪裏發出來的?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:06.25,0:02:07.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:16.40,0:02:19.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在警戒區內的確沒有發現可疑人物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:20.60,0:02:24.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為，自己看不見自己啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:24.81,0:02:26.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,確認作戰成功
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:26.81,0:02:31.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,代號」00村上」繼續前往執行下一個任務
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:31.11,0:02:33.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,試著接近新目標
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:34.38,0:02:38.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,#17可洛洛俄羅斯紅茶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:40.12,0:02:42.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,梅爾優被職業殺手盯上了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:42.62,0:02:46.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是啊，據說那個殺手還是個狠角色
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:46.36,0:02:49.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是為什麼殺手會盯上梅爾優?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:49.10,0:02:54.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就文件資料顯示天使隊留下了不少戰績
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:54.14,0:02:55.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,其中一部分的評價還寫著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:55.44,0:02:59.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,幸運女孩梅爾優表現相當優異
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:59.97,0:03:04.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就算這樣，他們打算對梅爾優做什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:04.18,0:03:05.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,打擾了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:06.52,0:03:09.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是剛調派到整備課的凱薩·村上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:09.98,0:03:11.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以後還請各位多多照顧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:12.58,0:03:13.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,長得蠻帥的嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:13.89,0:03:16.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有什麼不懂的儘管問我吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:17.30,0:03:18.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,謝謝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:18.33,0:03:20.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們好好相處吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:20.20,0:03:21.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:21.33,0:03:23.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,目標，確認
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:26.67,0:03:28.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,職業殺手的五大誓詞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:28.77,0:03:33.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第一，為了計劃成功要進行綿密的調查
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:33.91,0:03:37.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第二，盡可能地接近目標
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:37.28,0:03:39.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,確實掌握目標的長相
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:39.85,0:03:45.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第三，調查活動務必小心謹慎千萬不可讓目標發現
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:47.59,0:03:50.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如影隨形的跟蹤目標
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:50.19,0:03:52.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不讓對方察覺觀察目標的行蹤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:52.66,0:03:55.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,當一切都掌握完畢之後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:55.53,0:03:57.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是她的死期到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:57.47,0:03:59.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,凡事得秘密進行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:59.70,0:04:01.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,話多將招致失敗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:02.60,0:04:07.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這句話的意思是\N要讓計劃成功，必須秘密地進行對吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:08.54,0:04:11.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請問一下你剛才聽到了什麼嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:11.45,0:04:14.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是「她的死期到了」之前嗎?還是之後?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:15.12,0:04:18.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很抱歉，知道我真正身份的人只有死路一條
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:18.95,0:04:22.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,咦?可是我根本不是人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:22.59,0:04:25.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只是一個剛好路過的情報員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:25.59,0:04:29.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,老大，我可以告訴你很多這裏的內幕情報喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:29.90,0:04:32.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我在工作時習慣單獨行動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:33.60,0:04:39.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,天使隊的很多幕後八卦\N還有不可告人的羞恥事耶…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:39.11,0:04:41.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為了達成任務請務必助我一臂之丈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:41.91,0:04:43.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒問題啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:45.85,0:04:48.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,香草，你怎麼了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:49.45,0:04:52.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,奇怪，諾麥德你換對象了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:52.15,0:04:56.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為剛來不太習慣，所以找諾麥德指導一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:57.79,0:05:02.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,天使隊的腦袋變成我的了\N已經沒什麼好怕的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:02.30,0:05:04.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣就能盡情觀察目標
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:05.40,0:05:07.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你想光明正大的待在人家房間裏對吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:07.77,0:05:09.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你怎麼這麼說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:09.57,0:05:11.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒有啦，我只是看你好像很開心．
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:11.94,0:05:15.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,盡可能地接近目標是基本中的基本
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:15.84,0:05:17.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一點粗茶，請用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:17.45,0:05:18.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是太感謝了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:18.88,0:05:21.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,突然來拜訪你，會不會讓你感到困擾?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:21.35,0:05:23.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果只是拜訪還好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:23.12,0:05:25.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是變態者的行為就有點…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:27.22,0:05:28.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼，我就不客氣了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:29.28,0:05:30.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:32.65,0:05:34.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是薩普利翁行星的健康茶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:34.43,0:05:39.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對啊，你好內行喔\N我最近迷上了健康食品
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:39.40,0:05:42.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,其實我也是超喜歡健康食品的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:42.17,0:05:44.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我還有這個喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:44.37,0:05:46.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,斯波朋行星的「如果如果的果實」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:47.58,0:05:49.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她真是個好人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:49.91,0:05:52.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還送了我一瓶維他命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:56.65,0:05:59.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我差點就斃了自己的情人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:00.26,0:06:03.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,情人?想不到你那麼早就出人頭地了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:05.89,0:06:07.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是，原諒我吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:07.33,0:06:12.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不論我們多麼相愛，只要接到命令我就得下手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:12.90,0:06:14.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為這是我的宿命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:14.90,0:06:19.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你何必那麼在意呢?對方根本對你沒意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:24.50,0:06:25.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雖然來這裏沒多久
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:25.55,0:06:28.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今天我就要…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:28.72,0:06:31.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂，梅爾優你額頭上開了一個洞耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:31.75,0:06:33.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,咦?真的嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:33.42,0:06:36.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,難看死了，用0K繃貼住吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:36.96,0:06:39.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣就不會難看了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:41.26,0:06:44.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂，這裏有教即使頭被打爆也能復活的咒語嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:44.57,0:06:45.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不知道耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:45.73,0:06:47.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,難道是這把槍有什麼問題?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:47.67,0:06:49.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我跟你們說，前些時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:53.51,0:06:55.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,槍果然沒有問題
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:55.61,0:06:57.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼?為什麼突然會這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:57.98,0:07:00.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好啦，快把鼻涕擦一擦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:00.48,0:07:01.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,村上先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:01.75,0:07:04.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,央優行星的那個到手了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:04.52,0:07:06.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有空的話，要不要來吃吃看?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:06.42,0:07:08.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,咦?那個夢幻極品嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:08.46,0:07:09.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對，就是那個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:09.99,0:07:13.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒錯，幸好我失手了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:13.33,0:07:15.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼可以射殺這麼棒的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:15.80,0:07:18.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對，這種人應該
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:18.20,0:07:20.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,用棒子槌死才對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:23.34,0:07:24.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為．．．為什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:24.91,0:07:28.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我使用的武器明明就沒有問題啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:28.81,0:07:32.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可惡，既然這樣就用這種一顆就能毒死大象的劇毒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:32.81,0:07:36.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,梅爾優，亞西貝行星的那個到手了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:36.68,0:07:37.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要不要試試看?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:37.85,0:07:39.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真的可以給我嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:42.12,0:07:44.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,總感覺身體變得健康多了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:47.16,0:07:49.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是一場夢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:49.30,0:07:51.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一定是一場惡夢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:51.67,0:07:55.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不面對現實的話，凡事都無法前進喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:13.15,0:08:15.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,眼前一片血紅．
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:15.42,0:08:17.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,下一招，進行下一招
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:17.26,0:08:21.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,華克中校那麼努力的表現，至少也要嘉勉他一下吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:22.46,0:08:25.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不行，再這樣下去會沒完沒了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:26.72,0:08:27.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,該怎麼辦呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:27.30,0:08:29.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這時候就需要這個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:29.77,0:08:33.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們的老師能為你指點迷津喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:33.71,0:08:36.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,歡迎來到我的咨詢室
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:36.44,0:08:40.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好，把一切告訴老師讓老師幫你做主吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:40.78,0:08:41.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼首先
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:41.85,0:08:44.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請把你少年時代的痛苦回憶告訴我吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:44.82,0:08:46.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,咦?為什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:46.29,0:08:49.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,老師是專家，提起勇氣說出來吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:49.89,0:08:51.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想想看喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:51.99,0:08:53.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,暑假的自由研究
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:53.56,0:08:54.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,把根莖植物養爛了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:55.67,0:08:58.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我拿了一根蔥去代替結果被大家取笑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:59.40,0:09:00.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我要開槍喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:00.64,0:09:02.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看來氣氛已經炒熱了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:02.97,0:09:04.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,總覺得與你的鴻溝越來越深
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:04.67,0:09:08.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,總是跟花鳥講話個性有點內向的說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:08.58,0:09:11.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,總之，現在你需要的是登山健行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:11.55,0:09:12.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:12.11,0:09:14.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒錯，就是登山健行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:15.54,0:09:17.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,登山健行啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:17.52,0:09:19.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,咦?登山健行嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:19.52,0:09:24.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,其實我這次假期正準備去爬「御嚴厲山」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:24.13,0:09:27.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是那座每年都傳出山難的超危險的山嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:27.53,0:09:30.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是天助我也不．．．請讓我跟你一起去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:30.77,0:09:31.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:33.39,0:09:35.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這真是個絕佳的登山大好天氣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:35.77,0:09:38.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是啊，一定會越來越健康
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:38.91,0:09:40.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請問
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:40.21,0:09:44.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼我非得陪你們來不可呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:44.11,0:09:47.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,想太多的話只會讓自己接下來更痛苦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:47.55,0:09:49.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼都不要想比較好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:49.98,0:09:51.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那我們走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:51.45,0:09:52.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:53.69,0:09:57.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今天一定要做好萬全準備殺了這傢伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:59.43,0:10:00.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,危險
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:02.10,0:10:03.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,中校，你不要緊吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:04.77,0:10:06.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好戲還在後頭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:06.67,0:10:07.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:07.57,0:10:08.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:11.47,0:10:14.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你怎麼了?已經累了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:14.34,0:10:16.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒有，只是有點頭昏眼花
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:16.54,0:10:17.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:20.31,0:10:22.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,總之，我們繼續趕路吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:22.88,0:10:22.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:22.92,0:10:26.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,山路總是有很多危險的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:26.79,0:10:30.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你說的沒錯大家要打起精神喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:30.76,0:10:32.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,當然，我就是這種打算
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:33.96,0:10:34.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:34.83,0:10:37.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼碰到那麼多慘事她依然還活著?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:37.50,0:10:41.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再跟你說一次我覺得中校也是個狠角色喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:43.50,0:10:45.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到了，這裏就是目的地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:48.28,0:10:51.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,終於只剩我們兩人了梅爾優
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:51.48,0:10:52.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不好意思來晚了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:52.95,0:10:55.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不曉得為什麼弓箭突然像暴雨般地射過來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:56.62,0:10:59.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,求求你，我想要你的命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:59.12,0:11:00.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,把你的人生給我好嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:02.28,0:11:03.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:03.49,0:11:04.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這我辦不到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:04.96,0:11:05.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:05.63,0:11:06.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:07.29,0:11:09.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒錯，這是不可能的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:10.69,0:11:11.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:12.17,0:11:15.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,梅爾優過度熱衷於健康食品
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:15.67,0:11:19.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有一天突然暴斃死亡了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:20.46,0:11:23.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼會這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:25.17,0:11:28.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還有，這是可魯波行星匹「耐耐本」健康食品
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:28.48,0:11:29.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還有這個…  變身
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:29.55,0:11:30.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,夠了，閉嘴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:30.95,0:11:34.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是一流的殺手盯上的獵物絕不讓它逃掉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:34.93,0:11:35.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:35.62,0:11:38.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,復活吧!梅爾優
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:38.46,0:11:41.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你很吵耶，你要搞到什麼時候啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:41.23,0:11:44.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他說不定是個好人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:45.71,0:11:47.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,猜拳十三奧義
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:47.44,0:11:49.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,開始羅，剪刀石頭布
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:49.77,0:11:51.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,鬍子紳士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:51.71,0:11:53.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你也有鬍子我也有鬍子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:53.27,0:11:55.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,明明大家都有鬍子為什麼要互相憎恨?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:57.16,0:12:00.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,#18復仇薑汁汽水
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:01.85,0:12:04.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,咦?我最近很冷淡?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:04.32,0:12:05.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:05.25,0:12:07.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這真是令人訝異啊，諾麥德
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:07.46,0:12:10.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我一向都很用心對人溫柔又體貼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:10.93,0:12:12.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真的是這樣嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:12.69,0:12:16.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,能不能請你確認一下你坐的地方?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:16.23,0:12:16.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:17.36,0:12:19.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哇!諾麥德你什麼時候跑來這裏的?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:19.83,0:12:22.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,從你來這裏的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:22.37,0:12:25.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你在的話就出聲說一下嘛哇，好噁心喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:25.17,0:12:27.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼好噁心?我是被害者耶．
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:27.54,0:12:29.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他們感情還是那麼好啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:29.98,0:12:31.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:31.88,0:12:34.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,反正走開啦，吵死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:36.18,0:12:38.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我現在要練習射擊忙得很呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:38.95,0:12:40.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你再繼續吵的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:40.59,0:12:42.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小心我讓你腦袋開花喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:42.89,0:12:43.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是夠了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:45.43,0:12:47.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂，你是故意的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:48.40,0:12:53.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,佛特對我施加的惡行最近越來越誇張了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:53.87,0:12:55.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,氣死我了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:55.40,0:12:58.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我一定要向她好好報這個仇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:58.77,0:13:00.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好感動喔，諾麥德
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:00.64,0:13:03.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,咦?你是烏丸千歲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:03.91,0:13:08.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,報仇，這兩個字聽起來實在太浪漫了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:08.18,0:13:10.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,咦?是嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:10.62,0:13:13.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是搞不懂年輕人的品味
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:13.55,0:13:15.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,諾麥德，求求你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:15.26,0:13:16.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請讓我幫你的忙吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:16.82,0:13:20.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請讓烏丸千歲盡點綿薄之力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:21.56,0:13:24.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那我能不能拜託你一件事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:24.17,0:13:26.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我一直很想要一樣東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:27.74,0:13:28.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小事一樁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:31.97,0:13:33.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂，站住
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:36.58,0:13:40.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒跟我打聲招呼你就想走過去嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:40.85,0:13:41.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂，你在看什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:42.42,0:13:45.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,本大爺的新手腳有那麼稀奇嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:45.32,0:13:47.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很羨慕是吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:47.72,0:13:49.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你嚇破膽了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:49.26,0:13:52.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你給我說說話啊，小佛特
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:52.66,0:13:56.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你這是幹嘛!反對暴力!反對暴力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:57.20,0:13:59.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,該怎麼說呢，你這小子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:00.10,0:14:01.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很礙眼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:07.21,0:14:09.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不可能，怎麼可能會這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:09.41,0:14:11.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我忙得要命，不要跟我講話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:12.17,0:14:13.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,諾麥德
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:13.11,0:14:14.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請振作一點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:14.58,0:14:19.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是我特地從倉庫拿出來的遺失文明」手腳伸展君」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:19.25,0:14:21.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你終於得到盼望已久的手腳怎麼還這樣．．．
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:21.59,0:14:25.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只是手腳變長了而已根本一點都不強嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:25.73,0:14:27.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,起來修行吧，諾麥德
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:27.76,0:14:31.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,努力修行總有一天一定要復仇雪恨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:31.43,0:14:32.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,向佛特·修特倫復仇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:33.70,0:14:36.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,給我記住，佛特·修特倫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:36.47,0:14:38.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂，我在這裏，在你後面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:20.48,0:15:21.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,成功了，諾麥德
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:22.54,0:15:25.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,無敗的冠軍此刻誕生了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:27.69,0:15:29.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,恭喜你，諾麥德
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:29.79,0:15:32.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,關於無敗冠軍的誕生請你發表一下感想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:35.67,0:15:36.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,接下來就是你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:36.33,0:15:37.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,佛特·修特倫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:40.43,0:15:42.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哼，有意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:47.17,0:15:49.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,終於來到這裏了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:49.58,0:15:54.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這麼一來，我跟諾麥德就能成功復仇了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:55.32,0:15:57.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哎呀，這可不行喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:57.89,0:15:58.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,誰？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:58.89,0:16:01.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可可莫，馬利普你們怎麼會來這裏?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:04.43,0:16:07.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,想一個人賺大錢這你就大錯特錯了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:07.90,0:16:10.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們會賺得比你以前更多
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:13.53,0:16:15.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,咦?千歲去了遠方?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:15.64,0:16:21.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是啊，她好像去找能承受跟你練習的超級練拳對像
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:21.48,0:16:25.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以今後你身邊的事就交給我們兩個來處理吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:25.48,0:16:27.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好，我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:30.32,0:16:32.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂，你們兩個這是幹嘛?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:32.62,0:16:35.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為這次是奪冠比賽啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:35.16,0:16:36.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,說不定可以撈一筆錢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:36.99,0:16:39.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不，我想說你一定很辛苦所以才．．．
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:39.86,0:16:43.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以瑣碎雜事都交給我們來處理
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:43.66,0:16:48.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你只要專心想比賽的事就好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:48.24,0:16:50.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們似乎另有目的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:50.67,0:16:53.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,算了，那就拜託你們羅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:54.17,0:16:55.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,起加油吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:56.74,0:17:00.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂，聽說了嗎?佛特好像是天使隊的隊長耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:00.41,0:17:03.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,咦?在街上幹架連贏200場的那個人嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:03.65,0:17:04.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真厲害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:04.89,0:17:06.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,去跟諾麥德說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:06.65,0:17:09.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我會一如往常的打得他跪地求饒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:09.46,0:17:13.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哼，我會讓她知道誰才是真正的冠軍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:25.11,0:17:27.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看來她也蠻有自信的嘛(諾麥德一點都不可怕)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:27.84,0:17:30.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過，諾麥德也調整到最佳狀態
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:30.74,0:17:32.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們也做好了萬全的準備
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:32.88,0:17:35.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,當然，但是為了慎重起見
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:35.72,0:17:36.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對不對?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:36.95,0:17:39.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,比賽前雙方的經紀人居然在這裏密商
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:39.65,0:17:42.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這要是被媒體知道了他們一定會很爽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:42.19,0:17:44.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你要跟我們談什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:48.93,0:17:50.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你要我們怎麼做?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:50.46,0:17:52.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我沒要你們做什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:52.27,0:17:57.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只要明天讓佛特·修特倫身體出狀況，不能好好比賽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:57.34,0:17:59.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,至於腳本就由你們來想吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:07.48,0:18:09.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們在做什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:09.88,0:18:10.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,佛特
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:10.82,0:18:13.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們準備了飲料給你喝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:13.39,0:18:14.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真不好意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:16.46,0:18:17.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,佛特
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:17.59,0:18:20.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,打倒你的人一定是我覺悟吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:20.63,0:18:22.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你這傢伙在說什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:29.24,0:18:30.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好燙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:40.52,0:18:44.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可惡，為什麼她狗屎運那麼好真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:44.85,0:18:47.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是受夠了(薄荷大小姐後援會聚會)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:49.27,0:18:51.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,薄荷大小姐，你到底怎麼了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:51.23,0:18:54.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今天不展露笑容給我們看嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:54.50,0:18:56.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為那個臭佛特
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:56.73,0:18:59.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,身體狀況一直不肯變差
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:00.87,0:19:05.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,既然這樣只能派軍隊直接攻擊她了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:05.87,0:19:07.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,派軍隊攻擊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:09.81,0:19:11.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂，你怎麼了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:11.68,0:19:14.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我回公司一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:22.92,0:19:25.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,您今天回來得真早啊，司令官大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:27.73,0:19:29.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:29.83,0:19:32.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,叫特科大隊出動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:32.17,0:19:34.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,目標是天使隊的佛特·修特倫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:34.84,0:19:36.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:37.20,0:19:39.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,少廢話，快給我出動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:46.11,0:19:47.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到底出了什麼事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:50.18,0:19:51.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是怎麼回事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:53.58,0:19:55.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,佛特受到軍方的攻擊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:55.72,0:19:59.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是啊，不過這跟我們無關
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:59.19,0:20:00.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對啊，對啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:00.23,0:20:02.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只是，她如果不能來這個會場
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:02.70,0:20:05.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,勝利就會自動變成我們的了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:14.61,0:20:18.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可惡，這麼密密麻麻一大堆到底是從哪裏冒出來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:26.69,0:20:29.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可惡，到此為止嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:40.30,0:20:41.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:42.40,0:20:44.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你躺在那裏幹嘛還不快點站起來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:44.77,0:20:47.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,諾麥德，你為什麼要救我?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:48.51,0:20:49.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不是說過了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:50.14,0:20:52.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,打倒你的人一定是我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:00.72,0:21:02.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,來，走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:02.62,0:21:03.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:04.69,0:21:07.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,首先要解決這些傢伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:07.13,0:21:08.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:08.63,0:21:09.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼，開始吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:09.76,0:21:10.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:18.21,0:21:21.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,佛特與諾麥德都沒來耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:21.61,0:21:22.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼可能來得了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:23.48,0:21:25.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他們兩個在跟軍隊打架耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:25.75,0:21:28.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是啊，就算佛特他們很能打
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:28.88,0:21:30.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也實在太魯莽了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:31.23,0:21:36.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不，我相信他們兩人一定會來這裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:36.29,0:21:38.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為．．．因為他們兩人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:38.46,0:21:41.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為了在拳擊場上對以往的恩怨做個了結
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:41.90,0:21:44.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,才拚命努力到今天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:44.77,0:21:46.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一定會來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:46.47,0:21:49.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我相信他們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:05.23,0:22:07.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好，開始吧，諾麥德
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:07.72,0:22:08.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:24.57,0:22:25.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,榻榻米會燃燒吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:25.77,0:22:27.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,當然會燃燒羅因為是用枯掉的稻草做的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:27.94,0:22:28.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,燒得超旺的(超萌的)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:28.74,0:22:29.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,遇上火災了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:29.71,0:22:30.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真叫人受不了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:30.61,0:22:31.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你吸到煙了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:31.61,0:22:32.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有一種「來了」的感覺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:32.81,0:22:33.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,消防車嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:33.58,0:22:34.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,覺得死了都無所謂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:35.20,0:22:36.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,既然消防車來了那就不要放棄啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:36.75,0:22:38.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只要有榻榻米，我什麼都不要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:38.45,0:22:40.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要這樣說嘛其它還有很多東西沒燒掉啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:40.39,0:22:42.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要氣餒努力活下去就會有好事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:42.92,0:22:46.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是幸福似神僊啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:46.46,0:22:47.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這麼快就恢復啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:48.10,0:22:49.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啟動認真模式
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:49.56,0:22:50.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不知道該怎麼辦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:51.36,0:22:52.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,超very緊張
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:52.57,0:22:54.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,心兒呯呯跳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:54.17,0:22:57.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,私奔極限
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:57.14,0:22:59.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,秘密進入
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:59.91,0:23:04.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,宛如軟綿綿的蛋白霜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:04.95,0:23:07.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,心跳加速
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:08.35,0:23:09.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,冰淇淋派
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:09.78,0:23:11.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,吻了你的心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:11.65,0:23:15.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快要溢出來的Jelly Beans
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:16.61,0:23:22.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,擁抱五彩繽紛的心情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:22.23,0:23:23.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,將音調調至Pop
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:23.93,0:23:27.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,剛采收的新鮮鼓動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:28.34,0:23:32.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一味地空轉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:32.57,0:23:37.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,活力爆炸
